        "heading": "",
        "heading_url": "",
        "heading_color": "#002855",
        "text": "<p class=\"font-size-14 line-height-140 font-sans-light\">From sunlit terrace lunches to intimate evening dinners, Mission Estate Restaurant is one of Napier’s premier dining destinations. Enjoy inspired seasonal menus, award-winning wines, and warm hospitality – all set within the timeless charm of New Zealand’s oldest winery. With only the freshest local produce used, the style of cuisine is contemporary fine dining with a European influence.<br><br></p>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-size-28 line-height-140 font-sans-bold\">Opening hours</h4>\n\n<div class=\"icon-wrapper font-size-12 line-height-120 font-sans-light\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M16.5 5V3m-9 2V3M3.25 8h17.5M3 10.044c0-2.115 0-3.173.436-3.981a3.9 3.9 0 0 1 1.748-1.651C6.04 4 7.16 4 9.4 4h5.2c2.24 0 3.36 0 4.216.412c.753.362 1.364.94 1.748 1.65c.436.81.436 1.868.436 3.983v4.912c0 2.115 0 3.173-.436 3.981a3.9 3.9 0 0 1-1.748 1.651C17.96 21 16.84 21 14.6 21H9.4c-2.24 0-3.36 0-4.216-.412a3.9 3.9 0 0 1-1.748-1.65C3 18.128 3 17.07 3 14.955z\"></path></svg> We're open 7 days for lunch and dinner\n</div>\n<div class=\"second-icon-wrapper icon-wrapper font-size-14 line-height-140 font-sans-light\">\n<div class=\"icon-col\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g fill=\"none\"><path d=\"m12.593 23.258l-.011.002l-.071.035l-.02.004l-.014-.004l-.071-.035q-.016-.005-.024.005l-.004.01l-.017.428l.005.02l.01.013l.104.074l.015.004l.012-.004l.104-.074l.012-.016l.004-.017l-.017-.427q-.004-.016-.017-.018m.265-.113l-.013.002l-.185.093l-.01.01l-.003.011l.018.43l.005.012l.008.007l.201.093q.019.005.029-.008l.004-.014l-.034-.614q-.005-.018-.02-.022m-.715.002a.02.02 0 0 0-.027.006l-.006.014l-.034.614q.001.018.017.024l.015-.002l.201-.093l.01-.008l.004-.011l.017-.43l-.003-.012l-.01-.0